## Laptop strain: same desktop bundle as workstation, plus laptop firmware bits.
## NOTE: no tlp. On 24.04 tlp CONFLICTS with power-profiles-daemon (pulled in by
## ubuntu-desktop-minimal) -> "held broken packages", and it would fight the
## mode-switcher, which drives power via powerprofilesctl (power-profiles-daemon).
## So laptop power management = power-profiles-daemon + distro-modectl's governor
## control: the GNOME-integrated, conflict-free path.
ubuntu-desktop-minimal
flatpak
gnome-shell-extensions
gnome-tweaks
gamemode
mangohud
winetricks
fwupd
laptop-detect
